    <part id="SpecSynAF-Part2">
        <titleStmt>
            <title>Language resource management — Syntactic annotation framework (SynAF) — Part 2: XML serialization</title>
            <abbr>ISOTiger</abbr>
        </titleStmt>
        <info type="description">
            <p>The second part of the SynAF standard is based on the previous version SynAF ISO 24615:2010, which was published in 2010. 
                SynAF ISO 24615:2010 includes a comprehensive reference model for the representation of syntactic annotations. Additionally, 
                the SynAF ISOTiger provides an XML serialization in Tiger format. The attributes in the XML serialization will have pointers to ISOCat.</p>
        </info>
